== Officers == The officers of ICPHS are [[Chao Gejin]] (President), [[Rosalind Hackett]] (Vice President), [[François Djindjian]] (Vice President), [[Luiz Oosterbeek]] (Secretary General), [[Franco Montanari]] (Treasurer), and [[Adama Samassékou]] (Past President).
== Publications == The ICPHS publishes the journal ''Diogène''/''[[Diogenes (journal)|Diogenes]]'' in French and English. It was founded in 1952 by [[Roger Caillois]]. For many years, [[Jean d'Ormesson]] was the Editor-in-Chief. Current Editors-in-Chief are [[Maurice Aymard]] and [[Luca Scarantino]].<ref>http://journals.sagepub.com/home/dio</ref>
